{"tid":1266811,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)莎賓娜的顫慄冒險 第1 2季","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T19:02:08.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74fe9a450c4ba494876ad6fe1ef3eba6b6be7487","tid":1266811,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=3d895c59\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=abb611c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c68d0a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/z2029969a/1540910839-2865474471_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fz2029969a%2F1540910839-2865474471_n.jpg&h=1fd9877b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://roteironerd.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/KIERNAMINI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Froteironerd.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2FKIERNAMINI.jpg&h=7f7a8ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據漫畫《莎賓娜的顫慄冒險》(The Chilling Adventures of Sabrina)改編新劇由Netflix接手開發，直接預定兩季，共20集。將與CW大熱新劇《河谷鎮》共處一個宇宙，兩劇都是根據阿奇漫畫改編。莎賓娜是阿奇漫畫中最受歡迎的角色之一，但沒有出現在《河谷鎮》裡。故事聚焦年輕女巫Sabrina Spellman，她半人半巫，致力於與威脅到她自己、家庭以及人類性命的邪惡勢力作鬥爭。充滿超自然、恐怖、魔法、巫術等元素，風格類似《羅斯瑪麗的嬰兒》和《驅魔人》<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d8581155\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=6e616be8\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf55f8f6554dea6ba6dc8b22176da05880a3b41e","tid":1266811,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc87ce1aa674925efd5074b1c82fec69c7c909e","tid":1266811,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67eb880bd912b876e2f7a7bff3b317f5b494926","tid":1266811,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0